<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Read Book Details</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fff8f0;
        }

        .read-page {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .left-section {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #f4f0e1;
            color: #3e3e3e;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            box-shadow: 4px 0 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .left-section h2 {
            color: #2d2d2d;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .left-section p {
            color: #3e3e3e;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .right-section {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: -4px 0 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .right-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2d2d2d;
        }

        .book-info {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }

        .book-info p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="read-page">
        <div class="left-section">
            <h2>Read Book Information</h2>
            <p>Here you can view the details of any book in your collection. You can check out the name, author, and price for all books stored in the system.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="right-section">
            <h2>Book Information</h2>
            <div class="book-info">
                <p><strong>Book Name:</strong> ERROR 404 </p>
                <p><strong>Author:</strong>ERROR 404</p>
                <p><strong>Price:</strong> ERROR 404</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
